  "text": "We should mention that not every modular invariant given in [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [Ka] can be realized by vertex operator algebra extensions of L sl 2 (k, 0) and L(c m , 0). It seems that the other modular invariants can be realized by vertex operator superalgebra extensions.",
